content: Fare delle immersioni alle Filippine è stato incredibile, però sono emozionata di tornare a Sydney adesso!
translations: eng:Diving in the Philippines was incredible, but I'm excited to be heading back to Sydney now
eng:Making a dive in the Philippines was incredible, but I'm excited about returning to Sydney now
